{"tid":1993730,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有關「天馬行動」，星島 或成最強文宣","createTime":"2020-04-29T03:35:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T06:52:58.000Z","uid":13160,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"fdc1d6b25c5f4ec4e1ab17a4742b34b5abbb3f94","tid":1993730,"uid":13160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:35:07.000Z","msg":"簡單goggle 一下「天馬行動」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eAW5114.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeAW5114.png&h=ee642161&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星島、港人港地、東網、文匯報 最先彈出黎<br />\n異口同聲形容示威者將會於5月1 施襲<br />\n佢地仲有詳細講時間、地點同襲擊行為<br />\n包括「預料會重演縱火堵路等暴力行徑，甚至引爆遙控炸彈，圖謀製造流血場面」<br />\n配合警方指香港有「恐怖主義」<br />\n<br />\n大佬 知唔知咩叫快閃<br />\n對家知得仲多你估會唔會重狗？<br />\n簡直係<span style=\"color: red;\">預約被捕</span>呀！<br />\n我唔希望手足因為咁比人拉<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">所以我呼籲大家5月1支持 五一黃金周 撐黃店就可以了</span><br />\n同時要照顧好身邊人 無人知當日會發生咩事<br />\n記住班狗係無人性架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">給天馬行動搞手的話：要快閃就靜靜雞、唔洗一早通天，同埋無人想知你快閃做啲咩</span>"},{"pid":"259243e676b186588ca5365a31935f0e9638d97d","tid":1993730,"uid":92188,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"咪中共產黨自編自導自演計<br />\n51去幫襯下黃店好過啦"},{"pid":"181b605982428704c68c136a84fa71b0c130579e","tid":1993730,"uid":13160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"259243e676b186588ca5365a31935f0e9638d97d","tid":1993730,"uid":92188,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"咪中共產黨自編自導自演計<br />\n51去幫襯下黃店好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:40:00.000Z","msg":"我就係咁既意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f346d0b48eb8804beb4602cb2171afc46df14d0","tid":1993730,"uid":53498,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:41:32.000Z","msg":"越睇越似党媒做嘅"},{"pid":"e2dc0e0dac2d34d861853e2c70a3801a2b0f9fd6","tid":1993730,"uid":13160,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1f346d0b48eb8804beb46